flowchart TD
    subgraph CM["Confusion matrix"]
        TP["TP True Positive Correctly predicted positive"]
        FP["FP False Positive Predicted positive — actually negative"]
        FN["FN False Negative Predicted negative — actually positive"]
        TN["TN True Negative Correctly predicted negative"]
    end
    PREC["`Precision = TP / (TP + FP) Of all predicted +, how many were right? Optimise when FP is costly (spam filter, legal screening)`"]
    REC["`Recall / Sensitivity = TP / (TP + FN) Of all actual +, how many did we catch? Optimise when FN is costly (cancer screening, fraud)`"]
    F1["`F1 Score = 2 × (P × R) / (P + R) Harmonic mean — balances both Use when classes are imbalanced`"]
    TP --> PREC & REC
    FP --> PREC
    FN --> REC
    PREC & REC --> F1
